        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样吧，我同时进行这三项测试，你们觉得如何？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没等研究员发出惊叹，我先一步往凯茜娅的脑门上弹了一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "太乱来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
